/END-FREE * P Configurator_loadPropertiesConfiguration... P E * *========================================================================= * Configures LOG4RPG from a properties file. Watches the properties * file for changes and reloads the configuration on changes. *========================================================================= P Configurator_loadAndWatchPropertiesConfiguration... P B export * D Configurator_loadAndWatchPropertiesConfiguration... D PI N D i_path const like(LOG4RPG_path_t ) D i_waitMinutes 10I 0 const options(*nopass) D i_unit 10A const options(*nopass) * * Parameter positions D p_waitMinutes C 2 D p_unit C 3 * - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - /FREE
