/END-FREE * P ProvisionNode_makeProvisionNode... P E * *========================================================================= R * ***PRIVATE *** (exported for internal use only) * Frees a provision node. *========================================================================= * Parameters: * io_hProvNode - Handle of the provision node as it was returned by * Logger_getLogger() or Logger_getRootLogger(). * * Returns: * void *========================================================================= P ProvisionNode_free... P B export * D ProvisionNode_free... D PI D io_hProvNode like(LOG4RPG_hLogger_t ) * * Helper fields D nodeName S like(LOG4RPG_loggerName_t) inz * * Node handle D provNode DS likeds(LOG4RPG_logger_t) D based(io_hProvNode) * - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - /FREE
