/END-FREE * P DebugMode_toString... P E * *========================================================================= * Tests, if the specified debug mode is valid (well known). *========================================================================= * Parameters: * i_debugMode - Debug mode as string. * * Returns: * isValid - Returns TRUE if the debug mode is known, else FALSE. *========================================================================= P DebugMode_isValid... P B export * D DebugMode_isValid... D PI N D i_debugMode const like(LOG4RPG_debugMode_t ) * - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - /FREE
if (i_debugMode = cLOG4RPG_DEBUG_QUIET) or B01 (i_debugMode = cLOG4RPG_DEBUG_OFF ) or (i_debugMode = cLOG4RPG_DEBUG_ON ) or (i_debugMode = cLOG4RPG_DEBUG_VERBOSE); return cTrue; else; return cFalse; endif;
/END-FREE * P DebugMode_isValid... P E *

