/END-FREE * P XMLLayout_format... P E * *=====================================================================* * Returns the header of this layout. *=====================================================================* * Parameters: * i_pHandle - Handle that is passed around the various calls to * this XMLLayout. * * Returns: * header - The header string of this layout. *=====================================================================* P XMLLayout_getHeader... P B export * D XMLLayout_getHeader... D PI like(LOG4RPG_header_t) D i_pHandle * const * * Helper fields D xmlString S like(LOG4RPG_header_t ) inz * * Layout handle D handle DS likeds(handle_t ) based(i_pHandle) * - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - /FREE
xmlString = //RADDAT '' + Layout_newLine();
xmlString = xmlString + '' + Layout_newLine();
xmlString = xmlString + '' + Layout_newLine();
return xmlString;
