/END-FREE * P XMLSocketAppender_doAppend... P E * *=====================================================================* * Used to set the properties of the appender. *=====================================================================* * Parameters: * i_pHandle - Handle that is passed around the various calls to * this XMLSocketAppender. * i_pPropsList - Handle of the property list that contains the * properties for the appender. * i_prefix - Prefix of the relevant property keys. * * Returns: * void *=====================================================================* P XMLSocketAppender_setProperties... P B export * D XMLSocketAppender_setProperties... D PI D i_pHandle * const D i_pPropList const like(LOG4RPG_pPropertyList_t ) D i_prefix const like(LOG4RPG_prefix_t ) * * Helper fields D oldCcsid S like(handle.ccsid) inz * * XMLSocketAppender-Handle D handle DS likeds(handle_t ) based(i_pHandle) * - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - /FREE
